        * tiny/tinylibb.el (w32-cygwin-path-to-dos): 1.56 Rewritten.
        (w32-cygwin-mount-table-dolist): 1.56 New.

        * tiny/tinylib.el (ti::p-perl-process-environment-macro): 1.57
