        * tinyadvice.el (Info-build-node-completions): 1.23 New.
        by Richard Y. Kim <ryk@dspwiz.com>
        (tinyadvice-:advice-table): 1.23 Added
        `Info-build-node-completions' for Emacs 19.x and 20.x
