        Added pp.el autoloads.

        * tinydired.el (tinydired-switch-to-ange-ftp-buffer): 1.13
        Byte compiler fix. Removed `use-prefix-key'

        * tinylibm.el (colours-supported-p): 1.32 Byte compiler fix.
        reference to free variable ver
