        highlight feature for XEmacs: `folding-mode-motion-highlight-fold'
        and package `mode-motion'. Suggested by
        Thomas Ruhnau <thomas.ruhnau@intermetall.de> 1999-08-31 (found
        the mail when I was purging old messages)
